<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="pt-BR">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<meta name="description" content="EU⁺ Vida — Você no comando da sua própria vida. Desenvolvimento humano com estrutura, profundidade e leveza.">
<title>EU⁺ Vida — Você no Comando da Sua Própria Vida</title>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Cormorant+Garamond:ital,wght@0,300;0,400;0,600;1,300;1,400&family=DM+Sans:wght@300;400;500&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
*, *::before, *::after { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }
:root {
  --bg:    #071220;
  --bg2:   #0C1A2E;
  --bg3:   #102238;
  --bg4:   #152A44;
  --blue:  #4A9BC4;
  --blue2: #7DC0E0;
  --text:  #EEF6FB;
  --muted: #6A9BB8;
  --border:  rgba(74,155,196,0.18);
  --border2: rgba(74,155,196,0.08);
}
html { scroll-behavior: smooth; }
body { font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif; background: var(--bg); color: var(--text); overflow-x: hidden; }
body::after { content: ''; position: fixed; inset: 0; background-image: url("data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg viewBox='0 0 512 512' xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%3E%3Cfilter id='g'%3E%3CfeTurbulence type='fractalNoise' baseFrequency='0.75' numOctaves='4' stitchTiles='stitch'/%3E%3C/filter%3E%3Crect width='100%25' height='100%25' filter='url(%23g)' opacity='0.035'/%3E%3C/svg%3E"); pointer-events: none; z-index: 0; }
h1, h2, h3 { font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif; line-height: 1.12; }
sup.plus { font-size: 0.5em; vertical-align: super; color: var(--blue); font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif; font-weight: 500; }
.container { max-width: 1080px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 0 28px; }

nav { position: fixed; top: 0; left: 0; right: 0; z-index: 100; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between; padding: 18px 40px; background: rgba(7,18,32,0.92); backdrop-filter: blur(16px); border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border); }
.nav-logo { font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif; font-size: 1.3rem; font-weight: 600; color: var(--text); text-decoration: none; letter-spacing: 0.02em; }
.nav-logo .frente { color: var(--blue); }
.nav-back { display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 7px; font-size: 0.75rem; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: 0.1em; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--muted); text-decoration: none; border: 1px solid var(--border); padding: 7px 16px; border-radius: 2px; transition: all 0.2s; }
.nav-back:hover { color: var(--blue); border-color: rgba(74,155,196,0.4); }
.nav-burger { display: none; background: none; border: none; cursor: pointer; padding: 4px; color: var(--muted); }
.mob-nav { display: none; position: fixed; top: 62px; left: 0; right: 0; background: rgba(7,18,32,0.98); border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border); padding: 20px 28px; flex-direction: column; gap: 0; z-index: 99; }
.mob-nav.open { display: flex; }
.mob-nav a { font-size: 0.85rem; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: 0.1em; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--muted); text-decoration: none; padding: 13px 0; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border2); transition: color 0.2s; }
.mob-nav a:last-child { border-bottom: none; }
.mob-nav a:hover { color: var(--blue); }

.hero { min-height: 100vh; display: flex; align-items: center; padding-top: 62px; position: relative; overflow: hidden; }
.hero::before { content: ''; position: absolute; top: -100px; right: -200px; width: 700px; height: 700px; background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(74,155,196,0.14) 0%, transparent 60%); pointer-events: none; }
.hero::after { content: ''; position: absolute; right: 0; top: 0; bottom: 0; width: 3px; background: linear-gradient(to bottom, transparent, var(--blue), transparent); opacity: 0.5; }
.hero-inner { max-width: 760px; position: relative; z-index: 1; padding: 80px 0; }
.hero-eyebrow { display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 10px; font-size: 0.7rem; font-weight: 500; letter-spacing: 0.22em; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--blue); margin-bottom: 28px; }
.hero-eyebrow::before { content: ''; display: block; width: 28px; height: 1px; background: var(--blue); }
.hero h1 { font-size: clamp(2.8rem, 7vw, 5.5rem); font-weight: 300; color: var(--text); line-height: 1.06; margin-bottom: 24px; }
.hero h1 em { font-style: italic; color: var(--blue); }
.hero-sub { font-size: clamp(1rem, 2vw, 1.15rem); font-weight: 300; color: var(--muted); line-height: 1.78; max-width: 520px; margin-bottom: 48px; }
.hero-ctas { display: flex; gap: 16px; flex-wrap: wrap; align-items: center; }
.btn-primary { display: inline-block; font-size: 0.82rem; font-weight: 500; letter-spacing: 0.14em; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--bg); background: var(--blue); padding: 14px 32px; text-decoration: none; border: 1px solid var(--blue); transition: all 0.2s; border-radius: 2px; }
.btn-primary:hover { background: var(--blue2); border-color: var(--blue2); transform: translateY(-1px); }
.btn-outline { display: inline-block; font-size: 0.82rem; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: 0.12em; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--text); text-decoration: none; border: 1px solid rgba(238,246,251,0.2); padding: 14px 32px; transition: all 0.2s; border-radius: 2px; }
.btn-outline:hover { border-color: var(--blue); color: var(--blue); }
.hero-stats { display: flex; gap: 40px; flex-wrap: wrap; margin-top: 56px; padding-top: 40px; border-top: 1px solid var(--border2); }
.hero-stat-n { font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif; font-size: 2.2rem; font-weight: 400; color: var(--blue); line-height: 1; margin-bottom: 4px; }
.hero-stat-l { font-size: 0.75rem; font-weight: 300; color: var(--muted); line-height: 1.4; max-width: 120px; }

.sec { padding: 80px 0; position: relative; z-index: 1; }
.sec + .sec { border-top: 1px solid var(--border2); }
.sec-label { font-size: 0.68rem; font-weight: 500; letter-spacing: 0.18em; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--blue); margin-bottom: 16px; display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 10px; }
.sec-label::before { content: ''; display: block; width: 20px; height: 1px; background: var(--blue); }
.sec h2 { font-size: clamp(1.8rem, 4vw, 2.8rem); font-weight: 400; color: var(--text); margin-bottom: 14px; line-height: 1.12; }
.sec h2 em { font-style: italic; color: var(--blue); }
.sec-sub { font-size: 0.93rem; font-weight: 300; color: var(--muted); line-height: 1.75; max-width: 520px; margin-bottom: 52px; }

.dor-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(3,1fr); gap: 2px; }
.dor-item { background: var(--bg2); padding: 36px 28px; position: relative; overflow: hidden; transition: background 0.3s; }
.dor-item:first-child { border-radius: 3px 0 0 3px; }
.dor-item:last-child { border-radius: 0 3px 3px 0; }
.dor-item::before { content: ''; position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; right: 0; height: 2px; background: linear-gradient(90deg, transparent, var(--blue), transparent); opacity: 0; transition: opacity 0.3s; }
.dor-item:hover { background: var(--bg3); }
.dor-item:hover::before { opacity: 1; }
.dor-n { font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif; font-size: 3.5rem; font-weight: 300; font-style: italic; color: rgba(74,155,196,0.1); line-height: 1; margin-bottom: 18px; display: block; }
.dor-item h3 { font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif; font-size: 1.2rem; font-weight: 600; color: var(--text); margin-bottom: 12px; }
.dor-item p { font-size: 0.86rem; font-weight: 300; color: var(--muted); line-height: 1.72; }

.steps-wrap { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 2px; }
.step { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 72px 1fr; background: var(--bg2); overflow: hidden; border-radius: 2px; transition: background 0.2s; }
.step:hover { background: var(--bg3); }
.step-num { background: var(--bg3); border-right: 1px solid var(--border2); display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif; font-size: 1.8rem; font-weight: 300; font-style: italic; color: rgba(74,155,196,0.3); padding: 28px 0; transition: background 0.2s; }
.step:hover .step-num { background: var(--bg4); }
.step-body { padding: 28px 32px; }
.step-label { font-size: 0.62rem; font-weight: 500; letter-spacing: 0.14em; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--blue); margin-bottom: 8px; }
.step-body h3 { font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif; font-size: 1.25rem; font-weight: 600; color: var(--text); margin-bottom: 8px; }
.step-body p { font-size: 0.87rem; font-weight: 300; color: var(--muted); line-height: 1.72; }

.publico-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(3,1fr); gap: 14px; }
.pub-card { border: 1px solid var(--border2); border-radius: 3px; padding: 28px 22px; background: var(--bg2); transition: border-color 0.3s, transform 0.2s; position: relative; overflow: hidden; }
.pub-card::before { content: ''; position: absolute; bottom: 0; left: 0; width: 0; height: 2px; background: var(--blue); transition: width 0.3s; }
.pub-card:hover { border-color: rgba(74,155,196,0.35); transform: translateY(-2px); }
.pub-card:hover::before { width: 100%; }
.pub-icon { width: 40px; height: 40px; border: 1px solid var(--border); border-radius: 2px; background: var(--bg3); display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; color: var(--blue); margin-bottom: 16px; }
.pub-label { font-size: 0.62rem; font-weight: 500; letter-spacing: 0.12em; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--blue); margin-bottom: 8px; }
.pub-card h3 { font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif; font-size: 1.1rem; font-weight: 600; color: var(--text); margin-bottom: 8px; }
.pub-card p { font-size: 0.82rem; font-weight: 300; color: var(--muted); line-height: 1.65; }

.solucoes-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(2,1fr); gap: 12px; }
.sol-card { border: 1px solid var(--border2); border-radius: 3px; padding: 24px 22px; background: var(--bg2); display: flex; align-items: flex-start; gap: 16px; transition: border-color 0.25s, background 0.25s; }
.sol-card:hover { border-color: rgba(74,155,196,0.3); background: var(--bg3); }
.sol-dot { width: 8px; height: 8px; border-radius: 50%; border: 1px solid var(--blue); background: transparent; flex-shrink: 0; margin-top: 6px; transition: background 0.2s; }
.sol-card:hover .sol-dot { background: var(--blue); }
.sol-tag { font-size: 0.6rem; font-weight: 500; letter-spacing: 0.12em; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--blue); margin-bottom: 5px; }
.sol-card h3 { font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif; font-size: 1.05rem; font-weight: 600; color: var(--text); margin-bottom: 5px; line-height: 1.2; }
.sol-card p { font-size: 0.8rem; font-weight: 300; color: var(--muted); line-height: 1.6; }
.sol-status { font-size: 0.6rem; font-weight: 500; letter-spacing: 0.08em; text-transform: uppercase; padding: 2px 8px; border-radius: 2px; margin-top: 6px; display: inline-block; color: var(--blue); background: rgba(74,155,196,0.1); border: 1px solid rgba(74,155,196,0.22); }
.sol-status.dev { color: var(--muted); background: rgba(122,143,163,0.08); border-color: rgba(122,143,163,0.18); }

.cta-box { background: var(--bg2); border: 1px solid var(--border); border-radius: 3px; padding: 64px 52px; text-align: center; position: relative; overflow: hidden; }
.cta-box::before { content: ''; position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; right: 0; height: 3px; background: linear-gradient(90deg, transparent, var(--blue), transparent); }
.cta-box::after { content: ''; position: absolute; bottom: -100px; right: -100px; width: 400px; height: 400px; background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(74,155,196,0.08) 0%, transparent 65%); pointer-events: none; }
.cta-box h2 { font-size: clamp(1.8rem, 3.5vw, 2.8rem); font-weight: 400; margin-bottom: 16px; }
.cta-box p { font-size: 0.93rem; font-weight: 300; color: var(--muted); line-height: 1.75; max-width: 500px; margin: 0 auto 36px; }
.cta-form { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 12px; max-width: 440px; margin: 0 auto; text-align: left; }
.cta-form input, .cta-form select { background: rgba(12,26,46,0.8); border: 1px solid var(--border); color: var(--text); font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif; font-size: 0.9rem; font-weight: 300; padding: 13px 16px; border-radius: 2px; outline: none; transition: border-color 0.2s; width: 100%; }
.cta-form input:focus, .cta-form select:focus { border-color: var(--blue); }
.cta-form input::placeholder { color: rgba(238,246,251,0.2); }
.cta-form select { appearance: none; cursor: pointer; }
.cta-form select option { background: #0C1A2E; }
.cta-form button { background: var(--blue); color: var(--bg); border: none; padding: 14px; font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif; font-size: 0.85rem; font-weight: 500; letter-spacing: 0.12em; text-transform: uppercase; cursor: pointer; border-radius: 2px; transition: background 0.2s, transform 0.15s; }
.cta-form button:hover { background: var(--blue2); transform: translateY(-1px); }

footer { border-top: 1px solid var(--border); padding: 36px 0 28px; background: var(--bg2); position: relative; z-index: 1; }
footer::before { content: ''; position: absolute; top: -1px; left: 50%; transform: translateX(-50%); width: 80px; height: 2px; background: linear-gradient(90deg, transparent, var(--blue), transparent); }
.footer-inner { display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 16px; margin-bottom: 20px; }
.footer-logo { font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif; font-size: 1.05rem; font-weight: 400; color: var(--text); text-decoration: none; }
.footer-logo span { color: var(--blue); }
.footer-links { display: flex; gap: 20px; flex-wrap: wrap; }
.footer-links a { font-size: 0.78rem; font-weight: 300; color: var(--muted); text-decoration: none; transition: color 0.2s; }
.footer-links a:hover { color: var(--blue); }
.footer-bottom { border-top: 1px solid var(--border2); padding-top: 18px; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 10px; }
.footer-copy { font-size: 0.68rem; font-weight: 300; color: rgba(106,155,184,0.4); }
.footer-tag { font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif; font-size: 0.85rem; font-weight: 300; font-style: italic; color: rgba(74,155,196,0.4); }

.reveal { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(20px); transition: opacity 0.65s cubic-bezier(0.22,1,0.36,1), transform 0.65s cubic-bezier(0.22,1,0.36,1); }
.reveal.visible { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
.rd1 { transition-delay: 0.08s; } .rd2 { transition-delay: 0.16s; } .rd3 { transition-delay: 0.24s; } .rd4 { transition-delay: 0.32s; }

@media (max-width: 900px) {
  nav { padding: 16px 20px; }
  .nav-back span { display: none; }
  .nav-burger { display: block; }
  .dor-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
  .dor-item:first-child { border-radius: 3px 3px 0 0; }
  .dor-item:last-child { border-radius: 0 0 3px 3px; }
  .publico-grid, .solucoes-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
  .step { grid-template-columns: 52px 1fr; }
  .cta-box { padding: 40px 24px; }
  .footer-inner, .footer-bottom { flex-direction: column; align-items: flex-start; }
}
</style>
</head>
<body>

<nav>
  <a href="https://eumaisempresa.github.io/Eumais/frentes/index.html" class="nav-logo">EU<sup class="plus">+</sup> <span class="frente">Vida</span></a>
  <a href="https://eumaisempresa.github.io/Eumais/frentes/index.html" class="nav-back">
    <svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 14 14" fill="none"><path d="M9 2L4 7l5 5" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.3" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg>
    <span>Voltar ao portal</span>
  </a>
  <button class="nav-burger" id="nav-burger" aria-label="Menu" onclick="document.getElementById('mob').classList.toggle('open')">
    <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="none"><path d="M3 5h14M3 10h14M3 15h14" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.4" stroke-linecap="round"/></svg>
  </button>
</nav>

<div class="mob-nav" id="mob">
  <a href="#problema" onclick="document.getElementById('mob').classList.remove('open')">O problema</a>
  <a href="#como-funciona" onclick="document.getElementById('mob').classList.remove('open')">Como funciona</a>
  <a href="#para-quem" onclick="document.getElementById('mob').classList.remove('open')">Para quem</a>
  <a href="#solucoes" onclick="document.getElementById('mob').classList.remove('open')">Soluções</a>
  <a href="#contato" onclick="document.getElementById('mob').classList.remove('open')">Contato</a>
</div>

<section class="hero">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="hero-inner">
      <div class="hero-eyebrow reveal">EU⁺ Vida</div>
      <h1 class="reveal rd1">Você no comando<br>da sua <em>própria vida.</em></h1>
      <p class="hero-sub reveal rd2">Desenvolvimento humano com estrutura, profundidade e leveza. Ferramentas para autoconhecimento, equilíbrio e construção de um legado com intenção e maturidade.</p>
      <div class="hero-ctas reveal rd3">
        <a href="#contato" class="btn-primary">Fazer diagnóstico de maturidade</a>
        <a href="#solucoes" class="btn-outline">Ver soluções</a>
      </div>
      <div class="hero-stats reveal rd4">
        <div><div class="hero-stat-n">10+</div><div class="hero-stat-l">Soluções para desenvolvimento humano</div></div>
        <div><div class="hero-stat-n">PDI</div><div class="hero-stat-l">Plano vivo que evolui com você</div></div>
        <div><div class="hero-stat-n">0</div><div class="hero-stat-l">Motivação vazia ou coach genérico</div></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="sec" id="problema">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="sec-label reveal">O problema real</div>
    <h2 class="reveal rd1">Sucesso no trabalho,<br><em>vazio na vida.</em></h2>
    <p class="sec-sub reveal rd2">A maioria das pessoas sabe o que quer profissionalmente. Mas perde a saúde, os relacionamentos e o sentido de si mesma no caminho.</p>
    <div class="dor-grid">
      <div class="dor-item reveal"><span class="dor-n">01</span><h3>Sem direção clara</h3><p>Trabalha muito, entrega resultado, mas não sabe para onde está indo. A sensação de correr no lugar é real e desgastante.</p></div>
      <div class="dor-item reveal rd1"><span class="dor-n">02</span><h3>Energia no limite</h3><p>O corpo e a mente pedem pausa mas o sistema não para. Sem gestão de energia consciente, o esgotamento é questão de tempo.</p></div>
      <div class="dor-item reveal rd2"><span class="dor-n">03</span><h3>Legado sem intenção</h3><p>Os anos passam e a sensação de que poderia ter construído mais, com mais significado, vai crescendo silenciosamente.</p></div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="sec" id="como-funciona">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="sec-label reveal">O método</div>
    <h2 class="reveal rd1">Como funciona</h2>
    <p class="sec-sub reveal rd2">Três etapas para sair do modo automático e começar a construir com intenção e maturidade.</p>
    <div class="steps-wrap">
      <div class="step reveal"><div class="step-num">1</div><div class="step-body"><div class="step-label">Diagnóstico</div><h3>Leitura honesta de maturidade</h3><p>Avaliamos onde você está em todas as dimensões que importam — sem maquiar, sem inflar. Um diagnóstico real para decisões reais.</p></div></div>
      <div class="step reveal rd1"><div class="step-num">2</div><div class="step-body"><div class="step-label">PDI Vivo</div><h3>Plano que evolui com você</h3><p>Não é um checklist fixo. O Plano de Desenvolvimento Individual evolui conforme você executa — baseado em evidências, não em intenções.</p></div></div>
      <div class="step reveal rd2"><div class="step-num">3</div><div class="step-body"><div class="step-label">Evolução</div><h3>Legado construído com intenção</h3><p>Acompanhamento contínuo. Cada passo registrado vira patrimônio de carreira e de vida — rastreável, real e seu.</p></div></div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="sec" id="para-quem">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="sec-label reveal">Público</div>
    <h2 class="reveal rd1">Para quem é</h2>
    <p class="sec-sub reveal rd2">EU<sup class="plus">+</sup> Vida é para quem quer crescer com estrutura — não com sorte.</p>
    <div class="publico-grid">
      <div class="pub-card reveal">
        <div class="pub-icon"><svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 18 18" fill="none"><path d="M9 2L3 7v9h4v-5h4v5h4V7L9 2z" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.3" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg></div>
        <div class="pub-label">Transição de Carreira</div>
        <h3>Profissionais em mudança</h3>
        <p>Quem está mudando de área, buscando reposicionamento ou querendo crescer de gerente para diretor.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="pub-card reveal rd1">
        <div class="pub-icon"><svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 18 18" fill="none"><circle cx="9" cy="7" r="3.5" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.3"/><path d="M2 16c0-3.87 3.13-7 7-7s7 3.13 7 7" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.3" stroke-linecap="round"/></svg></div>
        <div class="pub-label">Liderança</div>
        <h3>Gestores em evolução executiva</h3>
        <p>Líderes que querem ampliar maturidade, influência e capacidade de entrega além do perímetro direto.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="pub-card reveal rd2">
        <div class="pub-icon"><svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 18 18" fill="none"><path d="M9 2v14M2 9h14" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.3" stroke-linecap="round"/><circle cx="9" cy="9" r="7" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.3"/></svg></div>
        <div class="pub-label">Legado</div>
        <h3>Pessoas que querem mais sentido</h3>
        <p>Quem já conquistou resultados mas sente que poderia construir algo com mais significado e permanência.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="sec" id="solucoes">
  <div class="container">
